%% Diagram: View counting pipeline
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    PLAYER[Video player] -->|playback heartbeat| INGEST[Event ingestion<br/>Kafka topic]
    INGEST --> VALIDATE[Validate<br/>min watch time, replay window]
    VALIDATE --> DEDUP[Dedup<br/>Bloom filter on hash<br/>video + user + IP + UA]
    DEDUP --> AGG[Stream aggregator<br/>Flink / Spark<br/>per-video counters]
    AGG --> WRITE[Counter store<br/>Cassandra / Bigtable]
    WRITE --> CACHE[Hot read cache<br/>Redis]
    CACHE --> READ[API: GET /videos/v/views]
    AGG --> FRAUD[Fraud signals<br/>same-IP rate, watch-time outliers]
